title: Seychelles CPI Transportation
description: The transportation sub-index of the CPI basket in Seychelles decreased to 153.67 points in October of 2022 from 153.87 points in September of 2022. CPI Transportation in Seychelles averaged 104.04 points from 2007 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 155.17 points in June of 2022 and a record low of 41.51 points in February of 2007. This page provides - Seychelles Cpi Transportation- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Bureau of Statistics, Seychelles
